{"tid":45474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉15歲女兒「與世隔絕」　被禁電視、智慧型手機","createTime":"2016-12-19T03:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T14:32:15.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a21acf3f3f471ef8c835ef7cd6d3cfd055fcd0c","tid":45474,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2218/d2218456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2218%2Fd2218456.jpg&h=26ee147d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲木村拓哉的長女心美已經是個15歲的少女。<br />\n<br />\n日本男星木村拓哉2000年與工藤靜香奉子成婚，育有2個女兒木村心美、木村光希。大女兒心美今年已經15歲，為了因應國際學校的要求，暑假到東京代官山的服飾店當實習生，除了謙虛態度廣受好評，她的私下生活也因同事的曝光引起關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAlHcbz.img?h=702&amp;w=1248&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=1026&amp;y=1105\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAlHcbz.img%3Fh%3D702%26w%3D1248%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D1026%26y%3D1105&h=e4e7036a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木村心美預計2017年就要到法國留學、進修長笛，因此決定在日本的最後一個暑假去實習。她剛報到時，並沒有特別讓店裡的同事知道自己是星二代，只是用開朗的模樣積極投入工作，還一次就將15名同事的名字都記了起來，是個相當聰明的女孩。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20151112/photo/bkn-20151112144624415-1112_00862_001_07b.jpg?20151112160634\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20151112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151112144624415-1112_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20151112160634&h=b6e473f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心美的同事表示，心美給人的第一印象是「單純的千金」，因為年紀小沒有化妝，看起來白白淨淨的，但相處下來倒是沒有什麼大小姐或星二代的嬌氣，還會帶便當跟同事一起吃，不說根本沒人知道她是木村拓哉的女兒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/H7xzuhQQBIY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FH7xzuhQQBIY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=e25dc2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n令人驚訝的是，木村心美的雙親雖然都是大明星，但她在家卻被禁止看電視，當同事聊起國民夯團「放浪兄弟」時，她一概不知。心美也沒有自己的智慧型手機，只有緊急連絡用的PHS手機在身上，被同事形容有「與世隔絕」的感覺，也可見木村夫婦對於女兒的保護。"},{"pid":"4d84e8a6f226aa567d1dff05d5fb98c1189ddb05","tid":45474,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  脫俗大小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  內心勁pure勁true"},{"pid":"d01f8280d326c6862c61101507b596c8571fc575","tid":45474,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"啲圖乜鳩"},{"pid":"b03694ed5b225c22265586195da95c09cc4dcc90","tid":45474,"uid":17527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"叫得心美既都係女神黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a82f945b82026ee5bcfa73a3a9ffc9161dbe93","tid":45474,"uid":34952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"個樣都好似黃心美"},{"pid":"097dbbb77ded8d57ac0743808754d48e88fef6f3","tid":45474,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"禁室培慾？"},{"pid":"3815f282b7e634953f9f59cd59ddcd009c918229","tid":45474,"uid":5055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"關伊巴咩事"},{"pid":"b28be3b3feda89283657aa1ad1b6b2f0994a18b2","tid":45474,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"好想做佢男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc20ecd70947ae04aeb61e0c4a43c6e1a042cde","tid":45474,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"d圖做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630f41e4c34bebfdd7297737bd877cd6c3b549a6","tid":45474,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"好有木村做日劇男主既feel"},{"pid":"9ecea9e4d3b4168cbadfc6f8f1745b62ae3cbb63","tid":45474,"uid":20943,"